0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:43:25.000Z","msg":"每日到到夜晚會覺得好孤單好辛苦好攰 好想開口問佢其實係咪想分手 但又會唔捨得怕一開口就返唔到轉頭<br />\n到到朝早就會諗又過左一日 我仲好愛佢 可能情況無自己諗得咁差 好彩無開口講"},{"pid":"6a2fc16cb7061496adeef5c629874df2303a81ee","tid":240173,"uid":45177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"整左個同佢既 ig <br />\n到三年個時送比佢<br />\n可能就係個一日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c4b43e253357a67cff602296b41474f09b6c0c","tid":240173,"uid":45177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e6ec290cbe3fce3f80169afa89015ca2da7981","tid":240173,"uid":50136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T10:11:38.000Z","msg":"中意就唔應該咁諗啦 咩諗法黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89c11d323e7be2da65091de22ad672ca9a473bd","tid":240173,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T10:13:12.000Z","msg":"完全明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔係將我放第一位<br />\n但對我黎講<br />\n佢係全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39cee47607b9c246e426c23b898ea217fa69837","tid":240173,"uid":24802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T10:15:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔係將我放第一位<br />\n但對我黎講<br />\n佢係全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我已經認得哂你地d名<br />\n你依家點啊"},{"pid":"399c60d38e4993063934556c05c0b497f42b0f2d","tid":240173,"uid":20882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>完全明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔係將我放第一位<br />\n但對我黎講<br />\n佢係全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我已經認得哂你地d名<br />\n你依家點啊</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我想留一次咁大把</span>"},{"pid":"8c9d9bdf8538d07f5b512e2ea556355f9c0ea002","tid":240173,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T10:23:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>完全明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔係將我放第一位<br />\n但對我黎講<br />\n佢係全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我已經認得哂你地d名<br />\n你依家點啊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個人on99 喺韓國9 fing<br />\n頭1 2 日好唔開心 行行下都會喺條街喊<br />\n但之後開始慢慢諗通<br />\n覺得我唔會同佢有將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為佢同樓主男朋友一樣<br />\n覺得我唔係最重要<br />\n對佢黎講 賺大錢揸波子先係no.1<br />\n我唔係佢努力既動力 亦都唔係佢上進既原因<br />\n<br />\n如果佢話 決定分手 咁就分啦<br />\n佢都無留我 我留喺度只會2個都辛苦<br />\n<br />\n如果佢話一齊返<br />\n我都會比最後一次機會佢<br />\n但都同自己講<br />\n如果一年都無改善<br />\n咁我都會走 連屋企人都叫我分手 唔好哂時間<br />\n我巳經比左18 19 20 歲佢<br />\n我可以再比埋21歲佢<br />\n但無將來既話 我唔想再浪費我既22歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14eeac0b807abfe9b2a20f383b59cdd1666e2c60","tid":240173,"uid":45177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T10:25:29.000Z","msg":"乜又係你地呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e719ad341176001f8cc51ba3c